{
  "stem": "13471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then he would take our board down to Second Ave, secretary of the Navy, one floor lower.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then-- I mean, Second Ave would take our board and go to the White House and brief FDR.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, I always wanted to go, I never got to go to the White House.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I kept hinting around, well, now, don't you think I ought to, I could-- well, anyway.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that's what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What street address?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- well, I was on US Highway One in Swarthmore, PA.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were gassing up the car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd stopped [LAUGHS] to gas up the car, and my brother was still sitting in the car with the radio going.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was, with the dipstick in the oil or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he stuck his head out the window, he said, the Japs bombed Pearl Harbor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh my God.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, everybody could tell exactly where they were in those days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went back to Washington.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was on my way back to Washington from a weekend away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by the time I got to Washington-- back in those days it was about a three-hour drive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a messy drive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I would convince myself, of course, that my services were absolutely essential here in the new war effort.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, Ensign.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They certainly weren't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I got inside the DC limits and called up the office.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, it was Sunday evening, about 5:00 or 6:00.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this very bored duty officer said, well, come in in the morning at normal times and we'll see what to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Big letdown, I wasn't all that important after all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's-- that's when I had this feeling.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
